{
  "chapter": 260,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙以沈良身份前往李园客居的听竹别馆拜访，被告知李园刚出门。归途中倍感寂寞，担忧韩闯与郭开联手出卖自己。清秀夫人派骑士邀他会面，两人同乘马车前往牛山一游。途中清秀夫人透露李园因楚相身份陷入两难，警告项少龙处境危险，劝他趁早离开临淄。项少龙谢绝好意，表示尚有责任未了。回到听松别馆后，董淑贞前来推拿，告知曲谱被偷的真凶是张泉而非小宁。董淑贞试探项少龙与韩闯的关系，又以暧昧言辞挑逗。正欲亲近时，侍从来报解子元提前到访，令项少龙心生警觉。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_guan",
      "speaker_name": "门官",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "原来是沈大爷，相爷早有吩咐，不过相爷刚出门，沈爷有没有口讯留下呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "烦请告知相国我来过便成。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "骑士",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这位兄台怎么称呼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qi_shi",
      "text": "有什么事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_shi",
      "speaker_name": "骑士",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "敝主人是清秀夫人，小人奉她之命前来请先生往会，因夫人没有把先生的高姓大名告诉小人，才会冒昧相询。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上将军你好！请坐到清秀身旁来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上将军的装扮很奥妙，若非清秀从李相爷处得知上将军来了临淄，恐怕认不出来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "希望李相爷不会逢人便说我来了齐国才好。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "李相爷怎会是如此不知轻重的人，只因清秀乃琴太傅的至交好友，所以才不瞒人家吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "我尚以为夫人与李相爷的关系不大好哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "又下雪了，只不知牛山现在是何情景，上将军有兴趣陪清秀到那处一游吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "牛山？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "清秀少时曾随先父到过牛山，时值阳春三月，淄水湍湍，泉水从山隙间流泻而出，潺流跌宕，水气蒸腾，如雨似雾，望之宛若霏霏烟雨，到今天仍然印象深刻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "清秀很怕重游一些曾留下美好印象的胜地美景，因为深怕与心中所记忆的不符。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "那今天为何重游旧地？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我自己都不明白，或者是因有名震天下的项少龙相陪吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "原来项某在夫人心中竟有点分量。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "刚才妾身见上将军形单影只地站在府门处，比对起上将军在咸阳的前呼后拥，竟生出沧海桑田、事过境迁的感触。最后忍不住停下车来与上将军一见，上将军会因此笑人家吗？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "原来夫人竟对项某生出同情之意。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不是同情，而是怜惜，上将军可知自己的处境非常危险吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人此话必有依据，少龙洗耳恭听。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上将军的洒脱和不在乎己身安危的态度，乃清秀生平罕遇，就算不看在琴太傅面上，清秀也要助你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "你这些侍卫靠得住吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上将军放心，他们都是随侍妾身十多年的家将，况且他们根本不会想到你是项少龙哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "昨天李相爷入宫找我的妹子宁夫人，神情困苦，在妾身私下追问，才说出你的事来。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "那就糟了，他还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他哪会真的向妾身倾吐，但妾身可肯定他确把上将军视为肝胆之交。问题是他身为楚相，很多时都得把个人得失爱恶抛在一旁，处处以国事大局为重，否则何须苦恼？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若非是这等天气，妾身会趁现在把车开往城外，劝上将军不如一走了之，干干净净。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "我尚有些责任未完成，不过纵有人要对付我，我亦不会束手就擒。唉！在夫人警告少龙之前，我已想到有这种情况出现的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "事实早证明项少龙是应付危险的能者，况且真正的情况如何，根本没有人知道，或者妾身只是白担心吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看！那就是辅助桓公称霸的名相管仲埋骨之处。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上将军，你……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "没有舟楫渡河，恐怕不能登山远眺！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们得回去哩！若妾身想找上将军，该怎办呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人最好不要牵涉在这事件内，生死有命，若老天爷不眷顾我项少龙，我又有什么法子，人算哪及天算。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_xiu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "清秀夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人算不及天算，上将军真看得开，妾身不再多事了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈管事不是生病了吧！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "老虎我都可打死两头，怎会有事呢？二小姐光临可是有何指教？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "吓死人哩！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "定要有什么事才可来找你吗？来！让我为你推拿，包保你睡得好。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "让我试试二小姐的高明手法。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "找到是谁把曲谱偷龙转凤了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "是小宁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈管事今回错了，偷的人是张泉，小宁曾见过他在附近鬼鬼祟祟的，入房后又见有些东西摆乱了，当时不以为意，给秀真问起才说出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "我不信，那只是小宁诿过于人吧！噢！这处捏得真舒服，我要睡了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要睡，你答应过人家的事有什么下文？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "尚未有机会和她说，明天告诉你好吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听说韩闯和你是老朋友，你会否帮他来害人家呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "和他只是有点交情吧！哪谈得上是老朋友，二小姐放心好了，只要我有一口气在，都会为二小姐尽力。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈良你为何语调悲观，以前胸有成竹的定力到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "世事每每出人意表，谁能真的胸有成竹，只是尽力而为，所以我才需要你们真心信任。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "原来你并不只是欢喜男人的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "谁说我欢喜男人呢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 260,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "空口白话有什么用？用行动来证明你是喜欢女人吧！",
